snippet.title: Depp ENDS Amber Heard's LIES as Waldman SCORES media VICTORY!
snippet.description:
Depp ENDS Amber Heard's LIES as Waldman SCORES media VICTORY! 

- Hiring Adam Waldman was the RIGHT MOVE, and what he does shows the power that social media has when taken into the right hands. THIS is the type of push that is necessary to fight this type of insanity we've been seeing; a "hearts and minds" push if you will.
